T1  - Energy-economy interactions in Mexico: A multiperiod general equilibrium model
AU  - Blitzer, Charles R.
AU  - Eckaus, Richard S.
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 21
IS  - 2
SP  - 259
EP  - 281
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/05/01/
